description: This Retractable USB Cable offers high speed data transfer for quickly uploading music, pictures, or videos to your iPod or iPhone's library and also offers the convenience of charging. The innovative retractable design cuts down on travel bulk and ensures the portability of your MP3 iPod player without tangled cable mess.The cable can also be connected to the iPod USB car charger for charging on-the-go. Compatible with iPhone & iPod models with dock connector and supports either USB 1.1 or 2.0.
title: iPod / iPhone USB Data Sync & Charger Retractable Cable
